window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Set in Mississippi during the Civil War and Reconstruction, <i>The Unvanquished</i> focuses on the Sartoris family, who, with their code of personal responsibility and courage, stand for the best of the Old South's traditions. </p> <p><b>As an added bonus, when you purchase our Audible Modern Vanguard production of William Faulkner's book, you'll also receive an exclusive Jim Atlas interview. This interview – where James Atlas interviews James Lee Burke about the life and work of William Faulkner – begins as soon as the audiobook ends. </b></p>"; 
